{"tid":1560133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃婆婆消息","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T05:57:45.000Z","uid":246148,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20e388901f9fb6050f8ac28644c39e849a6c84b1","tid":1560133,"uid":246148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:48:49.000Z","msg":"王婆婆在反送中運動同樣無役不與，直至 8 月 11 日在太古城地鐵站被警察制服在地後，從此失蹤，整整一個月了。<br />\n<br />\n由於王婆婆家住深圳河以北，而且沒有手機，只用電郵聯絡，我們擔心她已經被大陸公安以莫須有的罪名扣留。<br />\n<br />\n8 月下旬，當時英國領事館職員 SIMON 被大陸行政拘留，有議員曾經請保安局協助提供資訊，也順便請他們向大陸政府了解王婆婆的下落。當時保安局高層官員叫議員先向警署報人口失縱，於是於 8 月 31 日帶同資料到灣仔警署報案，報案編號為 WCHRN19042032。<br />\n<br />\n之後議員再請同一位保安局高層官員向大陸跟進王婆婆的下落，並<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">告知有網上消息指王婆婆被扣押在韶關的看守所，到今日差不多過了兩個星期都沒有回音。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據之前的個案，如果王婆婆真的身處大陸，那麼她一係就被扣押在看守所，一係就被禁止出境。<br />\n<br />\n曾經有人考慮過到韶關或廣東省內的看守所碰運氣尋人，但探訪者也有可能從此被盯上，無法評估風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以幫到黃婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57989ddeb6630bbd6a204c80b101aa7dd13fe2c","tid":1560133,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左殤台個牌為左碗飯，童星老監馮生都要做奶共狗鳥！！！<br />\n<br />\n為紀念燒死林彬而起嘅18樓C座，狗馮既係老監亦負責主要角色，啱啱居然勁做維撚狗，幫狗政Spin話831死人只係街邊八婆鳩吹出黎，又吹香港咁大城市死幾個人點會遮得到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩！！我愈聽愈以為轉左俾Mei西監製添！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>疑點1: </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大點解要cap圖唔直接放片？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點2: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解Cap既所有圖都唔見畜聾打人，直播又會見到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點3: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚簡單既事點解要封站兩日？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點4: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n連721都唔會4個部門一齊見記者，點解831會？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ad62771355eff739766b8016d3dd93b3cc323b1e","tid":1560133,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"好掛住支英國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c003bc0cd7015cbe53672a83e7923f05dc9ad2cd","tid":1560133,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落 打狗救人<br />\n五大訴求同手足都缺一不可"},{"pid":"2fa7be7f48f9a7d80b10cc05067610fdf3feaa02","tid":1560133,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落 打狗救人<br />\n五大訴求同手足都缺一不可"},{"pid":"4473d9a0977f7871cdc2c910728097760a98e738","tid":1560133,"uid":20117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"黃婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人鄉下係韶關可以靠人脈打探下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77a06eee3f34d16e3643f3342f81ae07e4ee713","tid":1560133,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":